						<handDesc hands="3">
							<summary>Italian semi-cursive scripts of the 18th century. <name type="person" role="scribe">Yehudah Ḥayim</name>: perhaps the copyist of the part of the manuscript: inscribed in the prefixed certificates, folios 1r-6r.</summary>
