									<locus from="1r" to="5v"/>, <locus from="6r" to="6r"/>, <locus from="7v" to="73r"/>- due to different hands.</p>
							</handNote>
						</handDesc>
						<additions>
							<p>Three sheḥitah certificates, on behalf of Yehuda Ḥayim of Citadella, dated 1757, given by Mordekhai ben Shim᾿on Ḥayim of Verona, Menaḥem ben Yitshaḳ of Verona, Ya᾿aḳov ben Yitsḥaḳ ben Menaḥem of Modena and Avraham Yisrael of Padua.</p>
						</additions>
